it.polimi.se2019.server.model.game

Class Match

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.se2019.server.model.game.Match
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Match
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Match class is the core and root of the game's Model . It contains all the structures used for the game to progress: weapons, power ups and ammo decks, killshot track, the map, the list of players and so on.
    Author:
    mattiamassarini,merklin,thisisferra.
    See Also:

        private void initGameField()
        Generate the game field: - the map is create calling the Map constructor, passing the mapId parameter. -weaponStack, powerUpStack and ammoStack are created here by reading the respective json files. The stacks are shuffled before the game starts.
